Preheat the oven to 180C/350F/Gas 4.Melt the butter in a small pan. Add the spinach and cook until wilted. Place into a small ovenproof dish.Crack the eggs into a bowl and carefully slide on top of the spinach. Pour over the cream and season well with salt and freshly ground black pepper.Place in the oven and bake for about 7-10 minutes, or until the eggs are just set. Serve immediately.